@startuml
title Authentication Flow (Google OAuth2 + JWT)

actor User
participant Browser
participant "API Gateway" as APIGW
participant "Auth Service" as Auth
participant "Google OAuth" as Google

User -> Browser : Click Login
Browser -> APIGW : /auth/google/login
APIGW -> Auth : Forward request
Auth -> Google : Redirect user

User -> Google : Login & Consent
Google -> Auth : Callback with code

Auth -> Auth : Generate JWT
Auth -> APIGW : Return token
APIGW -> Browser : Send JWT

Browser -> APIGW : API request (JWT)
APIGW -> Auth : Validate token
Auth --> APIGW : Valid

@enduml